body_html:
What is the output of
gcc --version
which gcc

Have you ever changed or altered the compilers on this machine?
Can you try this by passing the following flags to cmake?
cmake -DUSE_GLOG=OFF -DUSE_GFLAGS=OFF -DUSE_GLOO=OFF -DUSE_LEVELDB=OFF -DUSE_OPENCV=OFF -DUSE_LMDB=OFF -DUSE_NCCL=OFF -DUSE_NNPACK=OFF ..
